 The Bitcoin Standard is considered kind of the Bible

11:55.400 --> 11:57.800
 in the cryptocurrency space and the Bitcoin space

11:57.800 --> 12:01.760
 of just a very rigorous systematic explanation

12:01.760 --> 12:06.400
 of why Bitcoin, what is it, why should it be,

12:06.400 --> 12:07.480
 why is it good.

