 In the new book, you talk about Fiat Money,

12:17.560 --> 12:19.520
 which is another way to do money.

12:19.520 --> 12:22.640
 So obviously there's a lot of different ways to do money

12:22.640 --> 12:25.120
 and maybe you haven't discovered the best way to do money.

